    Megatron looked to the sky. It was noon, and he waited, alone, at the 
location where Kitkat had described. He raised his com link to his lips, 
"Kitkat, this is Megatron.....where in the blazes are you?!?!?!"
    Suddnely, the bushes shook and Aracnia stepped out. She was going to 
attend this meeting as well. "Thought I would keep you company, after all, 
were a team now."
